{"tid":2355884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台美明（7日）舉行軍事高層對話 中國氣炸強烈譴責！","createTime":"2021-01-06T11:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T12:40:20.000Z","uid":337052,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c21a2d186b9ae7bb01853b965cbb54d2dfcfef","tid":2355884,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">跳腳！美台明軍事對話 華春瑩：堅決反對並強烈譴責</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/06 16:38<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國務院在華府時間5日晚間公布，<span class=\"red\">美台將於台灣時間7日透過視訊進行政治軍事對話。中國外交部發言人華春瑩今（6日）對此表示，「堅決反對並予以強烈的譴責。」</span><br />\n<br />\n繼台美經濟繁榮伙伴對話後，美國國務院在華府時間5日晚間公布，美台將於台灣時間7日透過視訊進行政治軍事對話。美方會由國務院政軍局助卿庫珀（Clarke Cooper）代表參與，對話預計聚焦在區域情勢、台美軍事合作與軍售等議題，我方表示將會全力推動。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《環球時報》報導，中國外交部發言人華春瑩今日主持例行記者會，她聲稱，「美方這麼做將嚴重違反一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報的規定，中方對此堅決反對並予以強烈的譴責。」<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩還說：「台灣問題事關中國的主權和領土完整，涉及中國核心利益，是中美關係中最重要最敏感的問題。中方敦促美方切實恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，立即停止與台灣進行任何形式的官方往來和軍事聯繫，以免進一步損害台海穩定和中美關係。<span class=\"red\">中方將根據形勢的發展作出必要的反應，堅決地捍衛國家的主權安全利益。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3403099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3403099&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=9a655dfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3403099&h=5eaae0d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3403099</a>"},{"pid":"a0f1132fa67ab3c5c1991fbe04130279f44bc02c","tid":2355884,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"穩了 侵根本冇打算讓位"},{"pid":"2ee9e273e651c4b0b677e7a944b737e8584a7160","tid":2355884,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肯武統未"},{"pid":"4365e9460d557a00fc1bb1e7634aeb6381df551d","tid":2355884,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:49:50.000Z","msg":"又準備拎香港人出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7123e3cb99d6e1484215702888f70d46018ac30f","tid":2355884,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2730000/2732164/0822_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2730000%2F2732164%2F0822_1024.jpg&h=12554b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/117145216_615064492538087_8253529764118476224_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=ZaKQGgkZ6TsAX8qbgU2&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=5f56ff994b278166aeee2ca41d9a5eea&amp;oe=601C56E0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F117145216_615064492538087_8253529764118476224_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DZaKQGgkZ6TsAX8qbgU2%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D5f56ff994b278166aeee2ca41d9a5eea%26oe%3D601C56E0&h=05fc930a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b70feb03bc19259eed3e4684b99466c5a218322","tid":2355884,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美台突然要搞所謂政治軍事對話，華春瑩：中方堅決反對、強烈譴責</span></strong><br />\n來源：環球時報-環球網<br />\n<br />\n2021-01-06 15:39<br />\n<br />\n【環球時報-環球網報導記者張卉】據台灣&ldquo;中央社&rdquo;6日消息，美國國務院當地時間5日宣布，美台將於當地時間6日（北京時間7日）通過視頻形式進行所謂的&ldquo;政治軍事對話&rdquo;。對話預計聚焦在區域情勢、台美軍事合作與軍售等議題。對此，中國外交部發言人華春瑩在6日的例行記者會上表示，她也注意到有關報導。美方這麼做將嚴重違反一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報的規定，<span class=\"red\">中方對此堅決反對並予以強烈的譴責。</span><br />\n<br />\n華春瑩稱，台灣問題事關中國的主權和領土完整，涉及中國核心利益，是中美關係中最重要最敏感的問題。中方敦促美方切實恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，立即停止與台灣進行任何形式的官方往來和軍事聯繫，以免進一步損害台海穩定和中美關係。<span class=\"red\">中方將根據形勢的發展作出必要的反應，堅決地捍衛國家的主權安全利益。</span><br />\n<br />\n舉報我也說兩句責編：王怡"},{"pid":"cb73167476d768735d12b6968c226660d99ffc92","tid":2355884,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7123e3cb99d6e1484215702888f70d46018ac30f","tid":2355884,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2730000/2732164/0822_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2730000%2F2732164%2F0822_1024.jpg&h=12554b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/117145216_615064492538087_8253529764118476224_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=ZaKQGgkZ6TsAX8qbgU2&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=5f56ff994b278166aeee2ca41d9a5eea&amp;oe=601C56E0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F117145216_615064492538087_8253529764118476224_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DZaKQGgkZ6TsAX8qbgU2%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D5f56ff994b278166aeee2ca41d9a5eea%26oe%3D601C56E0&h=05fc930a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"地球拜登千祈唔好否定一中<br />\n<br />\n唔係嘅話支公會好失望<br />\n連登仔都會好驚訝<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">之後雙雙精神分裂入青山</span>"},{"pid":"8bf076216c3bd15ae7a29e818ce419a109e609e6","tid":2355884,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/232/5cadc8277757f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F232%2F5cadc8277757f.jpg&h=dc